  "doc_id": "38053",
  "text": "Conversely, previous studies have demonstrated that DKK1 suppressed cell growth and migration [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , suggesting that DKK1 may have diverse biological roles in distinct types of cancer cell. To date, few studies have been published regarding the role of DKK1 in NSCLC, and these have mainly focused on elucidating its diagnostic or prognostic value [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . Further studies are required to elucidate the mechanisms underlying the differential and relative expression of DKK1 in NSCLC.",
